trans-unit.source: Abstract base class for the channel dispatcher that accepts channels and associates them with a service.
trans-unit.target: Abstrakt basisklasse for kanalen dispatcher som godtar kanaler og tilordner dem til en tjeneste.

trans-unit.source: This is used by developers who want to keep the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programming model but replace the system-provided runtime.
trans-unit.target: Dette brukes av utviklere som ønsker å beholde den [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programming modell, men erstatte kjøretiden fra systemet.

trans-unit.source: Such applications will pull messages out of channels and handle them directly with user-defined dispatchers.
trans-unit.target: Slike programmer pull meldinger utenfor kanaler, og behandle dem direkte med brukerdefinerte restaurant.

trans-unit.source: To use ChannelDispatcherBase , create a class derived from it, extend <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> and override <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, adding instances of your class derived from ChannelDispatcherBase to <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk ChannelDispatcherBase ved å opprette en klasse som er avledet fra den, utvide <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>og overstyre <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, legge til forekomster av klassen som er avledet fra ChannelDispatcherBase til <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, associated with the ChannelDispatcherBase object are available for inspection or modification through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Listener%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> respectively.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>og <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, tilknyttede med ChannelDispatcherBase-objektet er tilgjengelige for inspection eller endringen via den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Listener%2A>og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A>henholdsvis.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Listener%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Attach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Detach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29> methods when adding or removing a ChannelDispatcherBase item from its <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>kall av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Attach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Detach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29>metoder ved å legge til eller fjerne et element ChannelDispatcherBase fra den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Detach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Attach%28System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase%29></xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.CloseInput%2A> during shutdown before closing InstanceContexts.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>kall av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.CloseInput%2A>under avslutning før du lukker InstanceContexts.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.CloseInput%2A></xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] uses this call to close datagram channels and wait for all messages to get to an InstanceContext.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]bruker kallet lukke datagram kanaler og venter på alle meldinger for å gå til en InstanceContext.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, attaches the channel dispatcher to a specific host.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, kan du knytter kanal dispatcher til en bestemt vert.

trans-unit.source: This method can only be set when the instance of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> is in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState> state, as this is the only state that is both mutable and not disposed.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan bare angis når forekomsten av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>er i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState>tilstand, fordi dette er den eneste tilstanden er både ruletemplatevariable og ikke fjernet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationState> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> calls this method when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> is added to its <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>kaller opp denne metoden når den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>legges til i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: This gives the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> a chance to hook events and inspect the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, and provides the value that should be returned from the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Dette gir den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>mulighet til å koble hendelser og inspisere den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, og angir verdien som skal returneres fra den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase.Host%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> object can have many <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> objects, each associated with a different <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> for that service.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>objekt kan ha mange <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>objekter hver knyttet til en annen <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>for tjenesten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: The host keeps a list of these <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> objects in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Verten har en liste over disse <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>objekter i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the channel listener associated with the channel dispatcher.
trans-unit.target: Henter kanallytteobjektet tilknyttet kanal dispatcher når overstyres i en avledet klasse.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> associates an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> whose channels and messages this <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> is dispatching.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>knytter en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>der kanaler og postmeldinger dette <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>fordeler.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener"></xref> associated with the channel dispatcher.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener"> </xref> tilknyttet kanal-meldingsfordeleren.
